            <div type="general">
               <head>General</head>
               <p xml:space="preserve">Medjez el Bab is a town in North West Tunisia, situated some 60km away from the capital Tunis. It is located in the plain of the river Medjerda and was inhabited during the Roman era already, bearing the name Membressa.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="researchHistory">
               <head>Research history</head>
               <p xml:space="preserve">To the best of our knowledge hitherto no research has been done on the dialect of Medjez el Bab, however this dialect is taken into consideration and examined within the TUNOCENT project.</p>
